#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:17
msgid "Process the batch"
msgstr "Proses batch"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:19
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Barcode app --> Operations` and select an "
"operation type (like delivery orders) grouped into batches. From here, "
"select the card for the appropriate batch transfer, and click "
"the :guilabel:`BATCH` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Barcode --> Operasi` dan pilih "
"jenis operasi (seperti pesanan pengiriman) yang dikelompokkan ke dalam "
"batch. Dari sini, pilih kartu untuk transfer batch yang sesuai, dan klik "
"tombol pintar :guilabel:`BATCH`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:None
msgid "The Delivery Orders page."
msgstr "Halaman Pesanan Pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:26
msgid ""
"On the batch transfer screen, the products in the picking are grouped by "
"location, and each line is color-coded to associate products in the same "
"picking together."
msgstr ""
"Pada layar transfer batch, produk dalam picking dikelompokkan berdasarkan "
"lokasi, dan setiap baris diberi kode warna untuk mengasosiasikan produk "
"dalam picking yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:29
msgid ""
"Then, follow the prompt to :guilabel:`Scan the source location` barcode for "
"the storage location of the first product. Scan the barcode for the product "
"and package to process the transfer. To record multiple quantities, click "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(edit)` icon, and enter the required "
"quantities for the picking."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, ikuti petunjuk untuk :guilabel:`Pindai lokasi sumber` barcode "
"untuk lokasi penyimpanan produk pertama. Pindai barcode untuk produk dan "
"paket untuk memproses transfer. Untuk mencatat beberapa jumlah, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(edit)`, dan masukkan jumlah yang diperlukan "
"untuk picking."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:34
msgid ""
"Repeat this for all products, and click the :guilabel:`Validate` button to "
"mark the transfer as :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr ""
"Ulangi ini untuk semua produk, dan klik tombol :guilabel:`Validasi` untuk "
"menandai transfer sebagai :guilabel:`Selesai`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:38
msgid ""
"After creating a batch transfer and assigning a package to a picking, Odoo "
"suggests the specified package by displaying the name *in italics* under the "
"product name, ensuring pickers place products into the correct boxes."
msgstr ""
"Po vytvoření dávkového převodu a přiřazení balíku k pickingu Odoo navrhuje "
"zadaný balík zobrazením názvu *kurzívou* pod názvem produktu, čímž "
"zajišťuje, že pickery umístí produkty do správných boxů."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:42
msgid ""
"Products from the same order are labeled with the same color on the left. "
"Completed pickings are highlighted in green."
msgstr ""
"Produkty ze stejné objednávky jsou označeny stejnou barvou vlevo. Dokončené "
"pickings jsou zvýrazněny zeleně."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:46
msgid ""
"In a batch transfer for 2 `Cabinet with Doors`, 3 `Acoustic Bloc Screens`, "
"and 4 `Four Person Desks`, the `3/3` and `4/4` :guilabel:`Units` indicate "
"that the last two product pickings are complete."
msgstr ""
"V dávkovém převodu pro 2 `Cabinet with Doors`, 3 `Acoustic Bloc Screens` a 4 "
"`Four Person Desks` značí `3/3` a `4/4` :guilabel:`Jednotek`, že poslední "
"dva pickings produktů jsou dokončeny."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:50
msgid ""
"`1/2` units of the `Cabinet with Doors` has already been picked, and after "
"scanning the product barcode for the second cabinet, Odoo prompts the user "
"to `Scan a serial number` to record the unique serial number "
"for :ref:`product tracking <inventory/product_management/enable-lots>`."
msgstr ""
"`1/2` jednotek `Cabinet with Doors` již bylo vychystáno a po naskenování "
"čárového kódu produktu pro druhou skříň Odoo vyzve uživatele k `Naskenování "
"sériového čísla` pro zaznamenání jedinečného sériového čísla pro "
":ref:`sledování produktu <inventory/product_management/enable-lots>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/process_transfers.rst:0
msgid "Products to be picked in barcode view."
msgstr "Produkty k vychystání v zobrazení čárového kódu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:3
msgid "Process receipts and deliveries with barcodes"
msgstr "Zpracování příjmů a dodávek s čárovými kódy"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:10
msgid ""
"The **Barcode** app can be used to process receipts, deliveries, and other "
"types of operations in real time using a barcode scanner or the Odoo mobile "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Barcode** dapat digunakan untuk memproses penerimaan, pengiriman, "
"dan jenis operasi lainnya secara real time menggunakan pemindai barcode atau "
"aplikasi seluler Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:13
msgid ""
"This makes it possible to process operations on the warehouse floor when "
"they happen, instead of having to wait to validate transfers from a "
"computer. This real-time processing ensures barcodes are accurately assigned "
"to the correct products, packaging, transfers, locations, and more, reducing "
"errors and keeping inventory data in sync."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini memungkinkan pemrosesan operasi di lantai gudang saat terjadi, alih-"
"alih harus menunggu untuk memvalidasi transfer dari komputer. Pemrosesan "
"real time ini memastikan barcode ditetapkan secara akurat ke produk, "
"kemasan, transfer, lokasi, dan lainnya yang benar, mengurangi kesalahan dan "
"menjaga data inventaris tetap sinkron."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:19
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/transfers_scratch.rst:13
msgid "Enable Barcode app"
msgstr "Aktivace aplikace Barcode"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:21
msgid ""
"To use the **Barcode** app to process transfers, it must be installed by "
"enabling the feature from the settings of the **Inventory** app."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan aplikasi **Barcode** untuk memproses transfer, aplikasi "
"tersebut harus diinstal dengan mengaktifkan fitur dari pengaturan aplikasi "
"**Inventaris**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:24
msgid ""
"To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Then, scroll down to the *Barcode* section, and select the "
"checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Barcode Scanner` feature."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Inventaris --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Kemudian, gulir ke bawah ke bagian *Barcode*, "
"dan centang kotak di sebelah fitur :guilabel:`Pemindai Barcode`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:28
msgid ""
"After the checkbox is selected, click :guilabel:`Save` at the top of the "
"page to save changes."
msgstr ""
"Setelah kotak dicentang, klik :guilabel:`Simpan` di bagian atas halaman "
"untuk menyimpan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:30
msgid ""
"After the page has refreshed, a new option is displayed under "
"the :guilabel:`Barcode Scanner` feature: :guilabel:`Barcode Nomenclature` "
"(with a corresponding drop-down menu). Select either:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah halaman disegarkan, opsi baru ditampilkan di bawah fitur "
":guilabel:`Pemindai Barcode`: :guilabel:`Nomenklatur Barcode` (dengan menu "
"tarik-turun yang sesuai). Pilih salah satu:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Nomenclature`: The barcode actions using UPC and EAN, "
"detailed in the default nomenclature list, are available for use. By "
"default, Odoo automatically handles UPC/EAN conversion."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nomenklatur Default`: Aksi barcode menggunakan UPC dan EAN, yang "
"dirinci dalam daftar nomenklatur default, tersedia untuk digunakan. Secara "
"default, Odoo secara otomatis menangani konversi UPC/EAN."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default GS1 Nomenclature`: Scan barcodes of sealed boxes and "
"identify essential product information, such as Global Trade Item Numbers "
"(GTINs), lot number, quantity information, and more."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nomenklatur GS1 Default`: Pindai barcode kotak tertutup dan "
"identifikasi informasi produk penting, seperti Global Trade Item Numbers "
"(GTIN), nomor lot, informasi kuantitas, dan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:40
msgid ""
"There is also a :guilabel:`Configure Product Barcodes` internal link arrow, "
"and a set of :guilabel:`Print` buttons for printing barcode commands and "
"operation types, as well as a barcode demo sheet."
msgstr ""
"Ada juga panah tautan internal :guilabel:`Konfigurasi Barcode Produk`, dan "
"serangkaian tombol :guilabel:`Cetak` untuk mencetak perintah barcode dan "
"jenis operasi, serta lembar demo barcode."

