#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet.rst:144
msgid ""
"Removal strategies also support :abbr:`LIFO (last in, first out)` "
"and :abbr:`FEFO (first expiry, first out)`, but they only impact which "
"product is first picked, not the valuation method. For example, you can pick "
"using LIFO, but using average cost for valuation, as LIFO is not allowed "
"by :abbr:`IFRS (International Financial Reporting Standards)`."
msgstr ""
"Strategi pengambilan juga mendukung :abbr:`LIFO (last in, first out)` dan "
":abbr:`FEFO (first expiry, first out)`, tetapi hanya memengaruhi produk mana "
"yang diambil terlebih dahulu, bukan metode penilaian. Misalnya, Anda dapat "
"mengambil menggunakan LIFO, tetapi menggunakan biaya rata-rata untuk "
"penilaian, karena LIFO tidak diizinkan oleh :abbr:`IFRS (International "
"Financial Reporting Standards)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet.rst:151
msgid "Inventory vs Accounting"
msgstr "Inventaris vs Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet.rst:155
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Inventory app </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` keeps "
"track of the inventory value in real time as you **receive and deliver "
"goods**. The reporting menu lets you analyze inventory quantities and values "
"by company, location, product, and more."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi :doc:`Inventaris </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` "
"melacak nilai inventaris secara real time saat Anda **menerima dan mengirim "
"barang**. Menu pelaporan memungkinkan Anda menganalisis kuantitas dan nilai "
"inventaris berdasarkan perusahaan, lokasi, produk, dan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet.rst:161
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Accounting app </applications/finance/accounting>` updates "
"accounts when you receive **invoices or bills**. Even though receipts and "
"invoices differ, it’s not practical for accountants to post journal entries "
"for every inventory movement. So, they post a closing entry to account for "
"the difference between what has been invoiced and received/delivered. This "
"closing process happens usually once a year for SMEs, or once a month for "
"larger companies."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi :doc:`Akuntansi </applications/finance/accounting>` memperbarui "
"akun saat Anda menerima **faktur atau tagihan**. Meskipun tanda terima dan "
"faktur berbeda, tidak praktis bagi akuntan untuk memposting entri jurnal "
"untuk setiap pergerakan inventaris. Jadi, mereka memposting entri penutupan "
"untuk memperhitungkan perbedaan antara apa yang telah difakturkan dan "
"diterima/dikirim. Proses penutupan ini biasanya terjadi setahun sekali untuk "
"UKM, atau sebulan sekali untuk perusahaan yang lebih besar."

