#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:39
msgid ""
"Next, set the :guilabel:`Costing Method` to either :guilabel:`First In First "
"Out (FIFO)` or :guilabel:`Average Cost (AVCO)`:"
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, atur :guilabel:`Metode Perhitungan Biaya` menjadi "
":guilabel:`First In First Out (FIFO)` atau :guilabel:`Average Cost (AVCO)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`First In First Out (FIFO)`: Inventory is valued, and the cost of "
"goods sold (COGS) is calculated by assuming the oldest items purchased are "
"the first ones sold, tracking costs by specific receipt lots. It's a precise "
"method for fluctuating costs, and requires tracking units by their entry "
"time (load/serial numbers) for accurate removal from stock."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`First In First Out (FIFO)`: Inventaris dinilai, dan harga pokok "
"penjualan (COGS) dihitung dengan mengasumsikan barang tertua yang dibeli "
"adalah yang pertama kali dijual, melacak biaya berdasarkan lot penerimaan "
"tertentu. Ini adalah metode yang tepat untuk biaya yang berfluktuasi, dan "
"memerlukan pelacakan unit berdasarkan waktu masuk (nomor muat/seri) untuk "
"penghapusan yang akurat dari stok."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average Cost (AVCO)`: Inventory value is calculated by "
"dynamically averaging the cost of all units in stock, updating with each new "
"purchase or manufacturing receipt to reflect fluctuating prices, making it "
"ideal for varied vendor costs, with the system automatically recalculating "
"the unit cost and value for assets and COGS. Odoo handles the math, "
"adjusting the average cost automatically as products are bought or sold, but "
"doesn't change it when products sell, only updating when new stock arrives "
"at a different price."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Average Cost (AVCO)`: Nilai inventaris dihitung dengan merata-"
"ratakan biaya semua unit dalam stok secara dinamis, diperbarui dengan setiap "
"pembelian baru atau tanda terima manufaktur untuk mencerminkan harga yang "
"berfluktuasi, menjadikannya ideal untuk biaya vendor yang bervariasi, dengan "
"sistem secara otomatis menghitung ulang biaya unit dan nilai untuk aset dan "
"COGS. Odoo menangani perhitungannya, menyesuaikan biaya rata-rata secara "
"otomatis saat produk dibeli atau dijual, tetapi tidak mengubahnya saat "
"produk dijual, hanya memperbarui saat stok baru tiba dengan harga yang "
"berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:53
msgid ""
"Next, set the :guilabel:`Inventory Valuation` field to :guilabel:`Perpetual "
"(at invoicing)`. This setting ensures that real-time journal entries are "
"created in the *Accounting* app whenever stock enters or leaves the "
"company's warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, atur bidang :guilabel:`Penilaian Inventaris` menjadi "
":guilabel:`Perpetual (at invoicing)`. Pengaturan ini memastikan bahwa entri "
"jurnal waktu-nyata dibuat dalam aplikasi *Akuntansi* setiap kali stok masuk "
"atau keluar dari gudang perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:60
msgid "Set up a scrap location and its scrap journal"
msgstr "Siapkan lokasi pembuangan dan jurnal pembuangannya"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:62
msgid ""
"Next, you must create or edit an existing scrap location. "
"Open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. Open an "
"existing location or create a new one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, Anda harus membuat atau mengedit lokasi pembuangan yang ada. "
"Buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Lokasi`. Buka "
"lokasi yang ada atau buat yang baru dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:67
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Locations` list is filtered to show only internal "
"locations. Remove this filter to view all locations, including *Inventory "
"Loss* locations."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, daftar :guilabel:`Lokasi` difilter untuk hanya menampilkan "
"lokasi internal. Hapus filter ini untuk melihat semua lokasi, termasuk "
"lokasi *Inventory Loss*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:70
msgid ""
"Update the :guilabel:`Location Type` field to select :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Loss`."
msgstr ""
"Perbarui bidang :guilabel:`Jenis Lokasi` untuk memilih :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Loss`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:72
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`Loss Account` by selecting the account used for "
"scrapped goods."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan :guilabel:`Akun Kerugian` dengan memilih akun yang digunakan untuk "
"barang yang dibuang."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:75
msgid ""
"The `WH/Scrap` location is an :guilabel:`Inventory Loss` location that uses "
"the `600001 Scrapped Goods` journal as its :guilabel:`Loss Account`."
msgstr ""
"Lokasi `WH/Scrap` adalah lokasi :guilabel:`Kerugian Inventaris` yang "
"menggunakan jurnal `600001 Scrapped Goods` sebagai :guilabel:`Akun Kerugian`-"
"nya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:0
msgid "Specify an Inventory Loss Location Type and a Loss Account."
msgstr "Tentukan Jenis Lokasi Kerugian Inventaris dan Akun Kerugian."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:84
msgid "Scrap products"
msgstr "Hapus produk"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:86
msgid ""
"After the product category and location are set up, :doc:`products can be "
"scrapped <../warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory>`. Be "
