msgstr ""
"Setelah kategori produk dan lokasi diatur, :doc:`produk dapat dihapus <../"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory>`. Pastikan untuk "
"memilih lokasi penghapusan di kolom :guilabel:`Lokasi Penghapusan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:91
msgid "`20` units of `Under-Eye Masks` are scrapped to `WH/Scrap`."
msgstr "`20` unit `Under-Eye Masks` dihapus ke `WH/Scrap`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:0
