#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:99
msgid "View scrapped products in the Profit and Loss report"
msgstr "Lihat produk yang dihapus di laporan Laba Rugi"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:101
msgid ""
"After products have been scrapped to the correct scrap location, view items "
"scrapped to it in the Profit and Loss report. "
"Open :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Reporting --> Profit and Loss`. To "
"view the scrap order in the report, under the :guilabel:`Gross Profit` "
"section, expand the :guilabel:`Expense` category. Search for the scrap "
"journal in the list and click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon next to the scrap account and select :guilabel:`General "
"Ledger`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah produk dihapus ke lokasi penghapusan yang benar, lihat item yang "
"dihapus ke lokasi tersebut di laporan Laba Rugi. Buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laba Rugi`. Untuk "
"melihat pesanan penghapusan dalam laporan, di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Laba "
"Kotor`, perluas kategori :guilabel:`Beban`. Cari jurnal penghapusan dalam "
"daftar dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(elipsis vertikal)` di "
"sebelah akun penghapusan dan pilih :guilabel:`Buku Besar`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:109
msgid ""
"`$100` worth of `Under-Eye Masks` appear as a debit in the Profit and Loss' "
"General Ledger."
msgstr ""
"`$100` senilai `Under-Eye Masks` muncul sebagai debit di Buku Besar Laba "
"Rugi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:0
msgid ""
"View the General Ledger to see scrapped items in the Profit and Loss report."
msgstr "Lihat Buku Besar untuk melihat item yang dihapus di laporan Laba Rugi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/scrapped_inventory_valuation.rst:115
