msgid ""
"A *package* is a physical container holding one or more products. Packages "
"can also be used to store items in bulk."
msgstr ""
"*Paket* adalah wadah fisik yang menampung satu atau lebih produk. Paket juga "
"dapat digunakan untuk menyimpan barang dalam jumlah besar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:10
msgid "Packages are commonly used for the following purposes:"
msgstr "Paket umumnya digunakan untuk tujuan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:12
msgid ""
":ref:`Grouping products to move them in bulk <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"pack>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Mengelompokkan produk untuk memindahkannya dalam jumlah besar "
"<inventory/warehouses_storage/pack>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Shipping to customers <inventory/warehouses_storage/package-type>`: "
"configure package types to align with shipping carriers' size and weight "
"requirements, streamlining the packing process, and ensuring compliance with "
"carrier shipping specifications."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pengiriman ke pelanggan <inventory/warehouses_storage/package-type>`: "
"konfigurasikan jenis paket agar sesuai dengan persyaratan ukuran dan berat "
"pengangkut pengiriman, menyederhanakan proses pengemasan, dan memastikan "
"kepatuhan terhadap spesifikasi pengiriman pengangkut."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:16
msgid "Storing items in bulk."
msgstr "Menyimpan barang dalam jumlah besar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:18
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Use` is a field on the package form in Odoo that is only "
"visible by enabling the :guilabel:`Batch, Wave & Cluster Transfers` "
"and :guilabel:`Packages` features (:menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Package Use` adalah kolom pada formulir paket di Odoo yang hanya "
"terlihat dengan mengaktifkan fitur :guilabel:`Batch, Wave & Cluster "
"Transfers` dan :guilabel:`Packages` (:menuselection:`Aplikasi Inventaris --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:22
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Package Use` field on a packages form is set "
"to :guilabel:`Disposable Box`. Change this field to :guilabel:`Reusable Box` "
"**only** when configuring packages for :ref:`cluster pickings <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/cluster-pack>`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, kolom :guilabel:`Package Use` pada formulir paket diatur ke "
":guilabel:`Disposable Box`. Ubah kolom ini menjadi :guilabel:`Reusable Box` "
"**hanya** ketika mengonfigurasi paket untuk :ref:`cluster pickings "
"<inventory/warehouses_storage/cluster-pack>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Type` is an optional feature used for :doc:`calculating "
"shipping cost <../../shipping_receiving/setup_configuration>`, based on real "
"shipping weight. Create package types to include the weight of the package "
"itself (e.g. boxes, pallets, other shipping containers) in shipping cost "
"calculations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Package Type` adalah fitur opsional yang digunakan untuk "
":doc:`menghitung biaya pengiriman <../../shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration>`, berdasarkan berat pengiriman aktual. Buat tipe paket "
"untuk menyertakan berat paket itu sendiri (misalnya kotak, palet, wadah "
"pengiriman lainnya) dalam perhitungan biaya pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:32
msgid ""
"While packages are commonly used in the :doc:`three-step delivery route "
"<../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>`, they can "
"be used in any workflow involving storable products."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun paket umumnya digunakan dalam :doc:`rute pengiriman tiga langkah "
"<../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>`, paket "
"dapat digunakan dalam alur kerja apa pun yang melibatkan produk yang dapat "
"disimpan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:41
msgid ""
"To use packages, first go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Operations` heading, activate "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` feature. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
