msgstr ""
"*Lokasi penyimpanan* memungkinkan produk disimpan di lokasi tertentu tempat "
"mereka dapat diambil, sementara *rute multi-langkah* mengaktifkan operasi "
"picking itu sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/cluster.rst:64
msgid "When finished, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Setelah selesai, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

