#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:107
msgid "Lots and serial numbers"
msgstr "Nomor lot dan seri"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:109
msgid ""
"Lots and serial numbers differentiate identical products and track "
"information like arrival or expiration dates. To enable this feature, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the *Traceability* heading, check the box beside :guilabel:`Lots & Serial "
"Numbers` to enable the feature."
msgstr ""
"Lot dan nomor seri membedakan produk yang identik dan melacak informasi "
"seperti tanggal kedatangan atau kedaluwarsa. Untuk mengaktifkan fitur ini, "
"buka :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bawah "
"heading *Ketertelusuran*, centang kotak di samping :guilabel:`Lot & Nomor "
"Seri` untuk mengaktifkan fitur tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:None
msgid "Enable lots and serial numbers."
msgstr "Aktifkan lot dan nomor seri."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:117
msgid ""
"Next, ensure the intended product is tracked by lots or serial numbers by "
"navigating to the product form through :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Products --> Products`, and selecting the desired product. On the product "
"form, switch to the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, and under "
"the :guilabel:`Tracking` field, select either the :guilabel:`By Unique "
"Serial Number` or :guilabel:`By Lots` options."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pastikan produk yang dimaksud dilacak berdasarkan nomor lot "
"atau serial dengan membuka formulir produk melalui "
":menuselection:`Inventaris --> Produk --> Produk`, dan pilih produk yang "
"diinginkan. Pada formulir produk, beralih ke tab :guilabel:`Inventaris`, dan "
"di bawah kolom :guilabel:`Pelacakan`, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Berdasarkan "
"Nomor Serial Unik` atau :guilabel:`Berdasarkan Lot`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:123
msgid ""
"After enabling the features, assign lot or serial numbers to products using "
"an :doc:`inventory adjustment <../warehouses_storage/inventory_management/"
"count_products>` or during :ref:`product reception <inventory/"
"product_management/assign-lots>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengaktifkan fitur tersebut, tetapkan nomor lot atau serial ke "
"produk menggunakan :doc:`penyesuaian inventaris <../warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/count_products>` atau selama :ref:`penerimaan produk "
"<inventory/product_management/assign-lots>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:128
msgid "Locations and routes"
msgstr "Lokasi dan rute"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:130
msgid ""
"**Storage locations** and **multi-step routes** are necessary features for "
"setting **all** types of removal strategies on a location. However, these "
"features are specifically required for the closest location removal "
"strategy, as it is applied at the location level."
msgstr ""
"**Lokasi penyimpanan** dan **rute multi-langkah** adalah fitur yang "
"diperlukan untuk mengatur **semua** jenis strategi penghapusan pada suatu "
"lokasi. Namun, fitur-fitur ini secara khusus diperlukan untuk strategi "
"penghapusan lokasi terdekat, karena diterapkan pada tingkat lokasi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:134
msgid ""
"To activate these features, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under the *Warehouse* heading, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Location` and :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` features."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan fitur-fitur ini, buka :menuselection:`Inventaris --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bawah heading *Gudang*, aktifkan fitur "
":guilabel:`Lokasi Penyimpanan` dan :guilabel:`Rute Multi-Langkah`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:None
msgid "Enable the locations and route features."
msgstr "Aktifkan fitur lokasi dan rute."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:144
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:166
msgid "Expiration date"
msgstr "Tanggal kadaluwarsa"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:146
msgid ""
"Enable the **expiration date** feature to track expiration dates, best-"
"before dates, removal dates, and alert dates on a lot or serial number by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan fitur **tanggal kedaluwarsa** untuk melacak tanggal kedaluwarsa, "
"tanggal terbaik sebelum, tanggal penghapusan, dan tanggal peringatan pada "
"lot atau nomor seri dengan membuka :menuselection:`Inventaris --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:150
msgid ""
"Under the *Traceability* heading, ensure the :guilabel:`Lots & Serial "
"Numbers` feature is selected, and then select the check box "
"for :guilabel:`Expiration Dates` to enable the feature."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah heading *Ketertelusuran*, pastikan fitur :guilabel:`Lot & Nomor "
"Seri` dipilih, kemudian centang kotak untuk :guilabel:`Tanggal Kedaluwarsa` "
"untuk mengaktifkan fitur tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:None
msgid "Enable expiration dates feature for FEFO."
msgstr "Aktifkan fitur tanggal kedaluwarsa untuk FEFO."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:161
msgid ""
"The *packages* feature is used to group products together and is required "
"for the least packages removal strategy."
msgstr ""
"Fitur *paket* digunakan untuk mengelompokkan produk bersama-sama dan "
"diperlukan untuk strategi penghapusan paket paling sedikit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:164
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"select the check box for the :guilabel:`Packages` feature."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan pilih "
"kotak centang untuk fitur :guilabel:`Paket`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:None
msgid "Enable the packages feature."
msgstr "Aktifkan fitur paket."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:171
msgid ":doc:`Packages <../product_management/configure/package>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Paket <../product_management/configure/package>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:172
msgid ":doc:`2-step delivery <daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pengiriman 2 langkah <daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:173
msgid ":doc:`3-step delivery <daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Pengiriman 3 langkah <daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:3
msgid "Closest location removal"
msgstr "Penghapusan lokasi terdekat"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:5
msgid ""
"For the *Closest Location* removal strategy, products are picked based on "
"the alphanumeric order of storage location titles."
msgstr ""
"Untuk strategi penghapusan *Lokasi Terdekat*, produk dipilih berdasarkan "
"urutan alfanumerik dari judul lokasi penyimpanan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:8
msgid ""
"The goal of this strategy is to save the warehouse worker from taking a long "
"journey to a farther shelf when the product is also available at a closer "
"location."
msgstr ""
"Tujuan dari strategi ini adalah menghemat perjalanan panjang pekerja gudang "
"ke rak yang lebih jauh ketika produk juga tersedia di lokasi yang lebih "
"dekat."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:13
msgid ""
"To understand *location sequence* in the closest removal strategy, consider "
"the following example:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memahami *urutan lokasi* dalam strategi penghapusan terdekat, "
"pertimbangkan contoh berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:16
msgid ""
"A product is stored in the following locations: `Shelf A/Pallet`, `Shelf A/"
"Rack 1`, and `Shelf A/Rack 2`."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah produk disimpan di lokasi berikut: `Shelf A/Pallet`, `Shelf A/Rack "
"1`, dan `Shelf A/Rack 2`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:None
msgid "Show a mockup of real storage location in a warehouse."
msgstr "Tampilkan mockup lokasi penyimpanan nyata di gudang."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:22
msgid ""
"The sublocation, `Pallet`, is on the ground level. Products stored here are "
"easier to retrieve, compared to requiring a forklift to reach `Rack 1` and "
"`Rack 2`. The storage locations were strategically named in alphabetic "
"order, based on ease of access."
msgstr ""
"Sublokasi, `Pallet`, berada di tingkat lantai. Produk yang disimpan di sini "
"lebih mudah diambil, dibandingkan dengan memerlukan forklift untuk mencapai "
"`Rack 1` dan `Rack 2`. Lokasi penyimpanan diberi nama secara strategis dalam "
"urutan abjad, berdasarkan kemudahan akses."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:27
msgid "Enabling the Closest Location removal strategy"
msgstr "Mengaktifkan strategi pengambilan Closest Location"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Storage locations** and **multi-step routes** are necessary features for "
"setting all types of removal strategies on a location. However, these "
"features are specifically required for the closest location removal strategy "
"since it is only applied at the location level."
msgstr ""
"**Lokasi penyimpanan** dan **rute multi-langkah** adalah fitur yang "
"diperlukan untuk mengatur semua jenis strategi pengambilan pada suatu "
"lokasi. Namun, fitur-fitur ini secara khusus diperlukan untuk strategi "
"pengambilan lokasi terdekat karena hanya diterapkan pada tingkat lokasi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:33
msgid ""
"To activate these features, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Warehouse` heading, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` and :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` "
"features. Be sure to :guilabel:`Save` your changes."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan fitur-fitur ini, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Inventaris --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di bawah judul "
":guilabel:`Warehouse`, aktifkan fitur :guilabel:`Storage Locations` dan "
":guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes`. Pastikan untuk :guilabel:`Save` perubahan "
"Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:None
msgid ""
"Enable Storage Locations and Multi-Step Routes in the inventory settings."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan Storage Locations dan Multi-Step Routes di pengaturan inventaris."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:43
msgid "Configure location names"
msgstr "Konfigurasi nama lokasi"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:45
msgid ""
"To configure location names, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. Then, "
"select an existing location, or click :guilabel:`New` to create a new one, "
"and then enter the desired name in the :guilabel:`Location Name` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi nama lokasi, mulailah dengan menavigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Lokasi`. Kemudian, "
"pilih lokasi yang ada, atau klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk membuat lokasi baru, "
"lalu masukkan nama yang diinginkan di kolom :guilabel:`Nama Lokasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:50
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:48
msgid "Set the removal strategy"
msgstr "Atur strategi pengambilan"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:52
msgid ""
"Once the locations are named in alphabetical order, based on their proximity "
"to the output or packing location, set the removal strategy on "
"the :ref:`parent location <inventory/location-hierarchy>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah lokasi diberi nama dalam urutan abjad, berdasarkan kedekatan mereka "
"dengan lokasi keluaran atau pengemasan, atur strategi pengambilan pada "
":ref:`lokasi induk <inventory/location-hierarchy>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:56
msgid ""
"To do that, in the :guilabel:`Locations` list, select the parent location of "
"the alphabetically named storage locations."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, dalam daftar :guilabel:`Lokasi`, pilih lokasi induk dari "
"lokasi penyimpanan yang diberi nama secara abjad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:59
msgid ""
"Doing so opens the form for the parent location. In the :guilabel:`Removal "
"Strategy` field, select :guilabel:`Closest Location`."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini akan membuka formulir untuk lokasi induk. Di kolom "
":guilabel:`Strategi Pengambilan`, pilih :guilabel:`Lokasi Terdekat`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:None
msgid "Set Closest Location as the location's removal strategy."
msgstr "Atur Closest Location sebagai strategi pengambilan lokasi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:66
msgid ""
"In a warehouse, the storage location `WH/Stock/Shelf 1` is located closest "
"to the packing area, where products retrieved from shelves are packed for "
"shipment. The popular product, `iPhone charger` is stored in three "
"locations, `WH/Stock/Shelf 1`, `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`, and `WH/Stock/Shelf 3`."
msgstr ""
"Di gudang, lokasi penyimpanan `WH/Stock/Shelf 1` terletak paling dekat "
"dengan area pengemasan, tempat produk yang diambil dari rak dikemas untuk "
"pengiriman. Produk populer, `iPhone charger` disimpan di tiga lokasi, `WH/"
"Stock/Shelf 1`, `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`, dan `WH/Stock/Shelf 3`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:71
msgid ""
"To use the closest location, set the removal strategy on the parent "
"location, `WH/Stock`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan lokasi terdekat, atur strategi pengambilan pada lokasi "
"induk, `WH/Stock`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:74
