"First Out)` is set as the :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy`."
msgstr ""
"Kemeja tersebut berasal dari kategori *All/Clothes*, di mana :abbr:`FIFO "
"(First In, First Out)` ditetapkan sebagai :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fifo.rst:115
msgid ""
"The white shirts are tracked :guilabel:`By Lots` in "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of the product form."
msgstr ""
"Kemeja putih dilacak :guilabel:`By Lots` di tab :guilabel:`Inventaris` pada "
"formulir produk."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fifo.rst:118
