"To do that, go to Odoo's :guilabel:`Apps` module, search for "
"the :guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping` module, and click :guilabel:`Activate` "
"to install it."
msgstr ""
"Setelah akun Starshipit disiapkan, integrasikan dengan database Odoo. Untuk "
"melakukannya, buka modul :guilabel:`Apps` Odoo, cari modul "
":guilabel:`Pengiriman Starshipit`, dan klik :guilabel:`Activate` untuk "
"menginstalnya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Starshipit Shipping module in the Odoo Apps module."
msgstr "Modul Pengiriman Starshipit di modul Aplikasi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:104
msgid "Configure a Starshipit delivery method"
msgstr "Konfigurasi metode pengiriman Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once installed, activate the feature by going to :menuselection:`Inventory --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shipping Connectors` "
"section, activate the :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector` option."
msgstr ""
"Setelah diinstal, aktifkan fitur dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bagian "
":guilabel:`Konektor Pengiriman`, aktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Konektor "
"Starshipit`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:110
msgid ""
"After activating :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` page, click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengaktifkan :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector`, klik tautan "
":guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping Methods` di bawah konektor yang terdaftar. "
"Setelah berada di halaman :guilabel:`Delivery Methods`, klik "
":guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Methods` can also be accessed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Delivery "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Methods` juga dapat diakses dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Delivery "
"Methods`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"Configure a Starshipit delivery method in Odoo by filling out the fields on "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` form as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi metode pengiriman Starshipit di Odoo dengan mengisi kolom-kolom "
"pada formulir :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Delivery Method`: type `Starshipit`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Delivery Method`: ketik `Starshipit`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Starshipit` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Penyedia`: pilih :guilabel:`Starshipit` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: assign or create the delivery product that "
"will appear on the sales order line when the cost of shipping is computed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produk Pengiriman`: tetapkan atau buat produk pengiriman yang "
"akan muncul pada baris sales order ketika biaya pengiriman dihitung."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:127
msgid ""
"The fields discussed in this section are specific to configuring Starshipit. "
"For more information about the other fields, refer to :doc:`../"
"setup_configuration`."
msgstr ""
"Kolom yang dibahas di bagian ini khusus untuk mengonfigurasi Starshipit. "
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang kolom lainnya, lihat :doc:`../"
"setup_configuration`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:130
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Starshipit Configuration` tab, fill out these fields:"
msgstr "Di tab :guilabel:`Konfigurasi Starshipit`, isi kolom berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Starshipit API Key`: enter the :abbr:`API (Application "
"Programming Interface)` key :ref:`obtained from Starshipit <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/star-api>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kunci API Starshipit`: masukkan kunci :abbr:`API (Application "
"Programming Interface)` yang :ref:`diperoleh dari Starshipit <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/star-api>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Starshipit Subscription Key`: enter the subscription key obtained "
"from the same place as the :ref:`API key <inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"api>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kunci Langganan Starshipit`: masukkan kunci langganan yang "
"diperoleh dari tempat yang sama dengan :ref:`kunci API <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/star-api>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Origin Address`: Enter the address where products are shipped "
"from. This field is crucial for calculating shipping rates "
"and :ref:`generating shipping labels <inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"label>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Alamat Asal`: Masukkan alamat dari mana produk dikirim. Kolom ini "
"penting untuk menghitung tarif pengiriman dan :ref:`menghasilkan label "
"pengiriman <inventory/shipping_receiving/star-label>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Package Type`: Set a default package type to include the "
"weight of the empty package when automatically calculating shipping rates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Paket Default`: Tetapkan jenis paket default untuk "
"menyertakan berat paket kosong saat menghitung tarif pengiriman secara "
"otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:143
msgid ""
"To set a default package type, the *Packages* feature **must** be enabled "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menetapkan jenis paket default, fitur *Paket* **harus** diaktifkan di "
":menuselection:`Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:146
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` icon at the "
"top of the page to save the changes."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` di bagian atas "
"halaman untuk menyimpan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:148
msgid ""
"To load the newly configured shipping products, click :guilabel:`Select a "
"service linked to your starshipit account` at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Starshipit Configuration` tab, and a :guilabel:`Choose "
"Starshipit Shipping Service` pop-up window appears. In "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Service` field, select the desired shipping service "
"for deliveries and returns from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memuat produk pengiriman yang baru dikonfigurasi, klik "
":guilabel:`Select a service linked to your starshipit account` di bagian "
"bawah tab :guilabel:`Starshipit Configuration`, dan jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Choose Starshipit Shipping Service` akan muncul. Di kolom "
":guilabel:`Delivery Service`, pilih layanan pengiriman yang diinginkan untuk "
"pengiriman dan pengembalian dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:154
msgid ""
"The list of services shown during initial configuration may be incomplete. "
"Starshipit determines service availability based on shipment details such as "
"the destination address and package weight, which are not yet available at "
"this stage. To select from the full list of services available for a "
"specific order, use the :guilabel:`Get more delivery methods` option "
"directly from the sales order. See :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"label` for details."
msgstr ""
"Daftar layanan yang ditampilkan selama konfigurasi awal mungkin tidak "
"lengkap. Starshipit menentukan ketersediaan layanan berdasarkan detail "
"pengiriman seperti alamat tujuan dan berat paket, yang belum tersedia pada "
"tahap ini. Untuk memilih dari daftar lengkap layanan yang tersedia untuk "
"pesanan tertentu, gunakan opsi :guilabel:`Get more delivery methods` "
"langsung dari sales order. Lihat :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"label` untuk detailnya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:160
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` and the selected delivery service populates in "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` and :guilabel:`Starshipit Service Code` "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Confirm` dan layanan pengiriman yang dipilih akan terisi di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Shipping Method` dan :guilabel:`Starshipit Service Code`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:163
msgid "Sample of a Starshipit shipping product configured in Odoo:"
msgstr "Contoh produk pengiriman Starshipit yang dikonfigurasi di Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Sendle: Sendle drop off`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sendle: Sendle drop off`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping Product`: `Sendle Delivery`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Produk Pengiriman`: `Sendle Delivery`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Starshipit Service Code`: `STANDARD-DROPOFF`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kode Layanan Starshipit`: `STANDARD-DROPOFF`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:174
msgid ""
"Starshipit does not provide test keys when a company tests the sending of a "
"package in Odoo. This means that if a package is created, the account may be "
"charged."
msgstr ""
"Starshipit tidak menyediakan kunci uji coba ketika perusahaan menguji "
"pengiriman paket di Odoo. Artinya, jika paket dibuat, akun mungkin akan "
"dikenakan biaya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:177
msgid ""
"Odoo has a built-in layer of protection against unwanted charges when using "
"test environments. Within a test environment, if a shipping method is used "
"to create labels, then those labels are immediately cancelled after creation "
"— this occurs automatically. Please note that depending on the shipping "
"provider being used, the account might be charged for printing label, unless "
"the order is cancelled manually on the couriers’s portal."
msgstr ""
"Odoo memiliki lapisan perlindungan bawaan terhadap biaya yang tidak "
"diinginkan saat menggunakan lingkungan uji coba. Dalam lingkungan uji coba, "
"jika metode pengiriman digunakan untuk membuat label, maka label tersebut "
"akan segera dibatalkan setelah dibuat — ini terjadi secara otomatis. Harap "
"dicatat bahwa tergantung pada penyedia pengiriman yang digunakan, akun "
"mungkin akan dikenakan biaya untuk mencetak label, kecuali pesanan "
"dibatalkan secara manual di portal kurir."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:184
msgid ""
"Switch between the test and production environment by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Environment` smart button at the top of the shipping method "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Beralih antara lingkungan uji coba dan produksi dengan mengklik tombol "
"pintar :guilabel:`Lingkungan` di bagian atas formulir metode pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:190
msgid "Generate a label with Starshipit"
msgstr "Menghasilkan label dengan Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:192
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation in Odoo, add the Starshipit shipping method by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Add shipping` button."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat penawaran di Odoo, tambahkan metode pengiriman Starshipit "
"dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Tambah pengiriman`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:196
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` pop-up window, select a Starshipit "
"shipping method in the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` field."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Add a shipping method`, pilih metode pengiriman "
"Starshipit di kolom :guilabel:`Shipping Method`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:199
msgid ""
"If the desired service is not available, click :guilabel:`Get more delivery "
"methods`. This sends the actual order details (including the destination "
"address, weight, and volume) to Starshipit, which returns the complete list "
"of services available for that specific shipment. A new Starshipit delivery "
"method is then created automatically and selected in the :guilabel:`Shipping "
"Method` field."
msgstr ""
"Jika layanan yang diinginkan tidak tersedia, klik :guilabel:`Get more "
"delivery methods`. Ini mengirimkan detail pesanan yang sebenarnya (termasuk "
"alamat tujuan, berat, dan volume) ke Starshipit, yang mengembalikan daftar "
"lengkap layanan yang tersedia untuk pengiriman spesifik tersebut. Metode "
"pengiriman Starshipit baru kemudian dibuat secara otomatis dan dipilih di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Shipping Method`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:204
msgid ""
"Calculate the shipping rate by clicking :guilabel:`Get rate`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Add` to include the cost of shipping to the sales order "
"line, labeled as the *delivery product*."
msgstr ""
"Hitung tarif pengiriman dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Get rate`. Terakhir, klik "
":guilabel:`Add` untuk menyertakan biaya pengiriman ke baris sales order, "
"yang diberi label sebagai *produk pengiriman*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:209
msgid ""
"Automatically calculate shipping costs for Starshipit in **both** Odoo "
"*Sales* and *eCommerce* applications."
msgstr ""
"Hitung biaya pengiriman secara otomatis untuk Starshipit di **kedua** "
"aplikasi Odoo *Penjualan* dan *eCommerce*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:212
msgid ""
"Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label documents are "
"automatically generated in the chatter, which includes the following:"
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, :guilabel:`Validate` pengiriman tersebut. Dokumen label pengiriman "
"secara otomatis dibuat di chatter, yang mencakup hal-hal berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:216
msgid ":guilabel:`Tracking number(s)` if the selected courier supports it."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nomor pelacakan` jika kurir yang dipilih mendukungnya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:217
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Return label(s)` if the Starshipit connector is configured for "
"returns."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Label retur` jika konektor Starshipit dikonfigurasi untuk retur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Example of a shipped order in Odoo."
msgstr "Contoh pesanan yang telah dikirim di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:224
msgid ""
"Package weight in Odoo is calculated by adding the weights of the products "
"plus the empty package saved in the database. Ensure the correct shipping "
"option is selected, as the package weight is not automatically verified."
msgstr ""
"Berat paket di Odoo dihitung dengan menambahkan berat produk ditambah paket "
"kosong yang disimpan di database. Pastikan opsi pengiriman yang benar "
"dipilih, karena berat paket tidak diverifikasi secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:228
msgid ""
"Verify the destination address, as Starshipit checks it when the order is "
"created."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi alamat tujuan, karena Starshipit memeriksanya saat pesanan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:230
msgid ""
"Finally, some couriers may require other information, such as an email "
"address or phone number. Please ensure that all necessary information are "
"set upon sending a shipping order."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, beberapa kurir mungkin memerlukan informasi lain, seperti alamat "
"email atau nomor telepon. Pastikan semua informasi yang diperlukan telah "
"diatur sebelum mengirim pesanan pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:234
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "Pengembalian"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:243
msgid "Starshipit allows returns with the following couriers:"
msgstr "Starshipit mengizinkan retur dengan kurir berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:237
msgid "Australia Post eParcel"
msgstr "Australia Post eParcel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:238
msgid "TNT"
msgstr "TNT"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:239
msgid "Couriers Please"
msgstr "Couriers Please"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:240
msgid "Aramex"
msgstr "Aramex"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:241
msgid "StarTrack"
msgstr "StarTrack"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:242
msgid "DHL Express"
msgstr "DHL Express"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:243
msgid "NZ Post Domestic"
msgstr "NZ Post Domestic"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:245
msgid ""
"This can be done by clicking the :guilabel:`Return` smart button on the "
"intended delivery order. If the selected courier supports returns, "
"the :guilabel:`Print Return Label` button will be available."
msgstr ""
"Ini dapat dilakukan dengan mengklik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Return` pada "
"surat jalan yang dimaksud. Jika kurir yang dipilih mendukung retur, tombol "
":guilabel:`Print Return Label` akan tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:250
msgid "Cancellations"
msgstr "Pembatalan"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:252
msgid ""
"If a delivery order is cancelled in Odoo, it will be automatically archived "
"in Starshipit. However, the cancellation will not be sent to the courier "
"itself, so make sure to log onto the courier's platform to handle the "
"cancellation manually."
msgstr ""
"Jika surat jalan dibatalkan di Odoo, surat jalan tersebut akan otomatis "
"diarsipkan di Starshipit. Namun, pembatalan tidak akan dikirim ke kurir itu "
"sendiri, jadi pastikan untuk masuk ke platform kurir tersebut untuk "
"menangani pembatalan secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:3
msgid "Third-party shipping carriers"
msgstr "Perusahaan jasa pengiriman pihak ketiga"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:10
msgid ""
"Users can link third-party shipping carriers to Odoo databases, in order to "
"verify carriers' delivery to specific addresses, :doc:`automatically "
"calculate shipping costs <../setup_configuration>`, and :doc:`generate "
"shipping labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna dapat menghubungkan perusahaan jasa pengiriman pihak ketiga ke "
"database Odoo, untuk memverifikasi pengiriman ke alamat tertentu, "
":doc:`menghitung biaya pengiriman secara otomatis <../setup_configuration>`, "
"dan :doc:`menghasilkan label pengiriman <labels>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:14
msgid ""
"In Odoo, shipping carriers can be applied to a sales order (SO), invoice, or "
"delivery order. For tips on resolving common issues when configuring "
"shipping connectors, skip to the :ref:`Troubleshooting <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/third-party-troubles>` section."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, perusahaan jasa pengiriman dapat diterapkan pada sales order (SO), "
"faktur, atau surat jalan. Untuk tips mengatasi masalah umum saat "
"mengonfigurasi konektor pengiriman, lanjut ke bagian :ref:`Pemecahan Masalah "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-troubles>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:20
msgid ":doc:`sendcloud_shipping`"
msgstr ":doc:`sendcloud_shipping`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:23
msgid "The following is a list of available shipping connectors in Odoo:"
msgstr "Berikut adalah daftar konektor pengiriman yang tersedia di Odoo:"

