#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:227
msgid ""
"After configuring the third-party carrier's :ref:`delivery method <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>` in Odoo, create or navigate "
"to a quotation by going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> "
"Quotations`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengonfigurasi :ref:`metode pengiriman <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-delivery-method>` pengangkut pihak ketiga di Odoo, buat atau "
"navigasi ke penawaran dengan membuka :menuselection:`aplikasi Penjualan --> "
"Pesanan --> Penawaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:234
msgid "Sales order"
msgstr "Sale order"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:236
msgid ""
"To assign a third-party shipping carrier, and get an estimated cost of "
"shipping, begin by going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> "
"Quotations`. Create or select an existing quotation, and add the cost of "
"shipping through a third-party carrier to a quotation, by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Add Shipping` button in the bottom-right corner of "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menetapkan pengangkut pengiriman pihak ketiga, dan mendapatkan "
"perkiraan biaya pengiriman, mulailah dengan membuka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Penjualan --> Pesanan --> Penawaran`. Buat atau pilih penawaran yang ada, "
"dan tambahkan biaya pengiriman melalui pengangkut pihak ketiga ke penawaran, "
"dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Tambahkan Pengiriman` di sudut kanan bawah "
"tab :guilabel:`Baris Pesanan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"Add shipping\" button at the bottom of a quotation."
msgstr "Tampilkan tombol \"Tambahkan pengiriman\" di bagian bawah penawaran."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:245
msgid ""
"In the resulting :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` pop-up window, select the "
"intended carrier from the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` drop-down menu. "
"The :guilabel:`Cost` field is automatically filled based on:"
msgstr ""
"Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Tambahkan metode pengiriman` yang muncul, "
"pilih pengangkut yang dimaksud dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Metode "
"Pengiriman`. Kolom :guilabel:`Biaya` secara otomatis terisi berdasarkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:249
msgid ""
"the amount specified in the :guilabel:`Total Order Weight` field (if it is "
"not provided, the sum of :ref:`product weights <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-weight>` in the order is used)"
msgstr ""
"jumlah yang ditentukan dalam kolom :guilabel:`Berat Total Pesanan` (jika "
"tidak tersedia, jumlah :ref:`berat produk <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-weight>` dalam pesanan digunakan)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:251
msgid ""
"the distance between the warehouse's :ref:`source address <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` and the customer's address."
msgstr ""
"jarak antara :ref:`alamat sumber <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"source-address>` gudang dan alamat pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:256
msgid ""
"After selecting a third-party provider in the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` "
"field, click :guilabel:`Get Rate` in the :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` "
"pop-up window to get the estimated cost through the shipping connector. "
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Add` button to add the delivery charge to the |"
"SO| or invoice."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memilih penyedia pihak ketiga di kolom :guilabel:`Metode "
"Pengiriman`, klik :guilabel:`Dapatkan Tarif` pada jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Tambahkan metode pengiriman` untuk mendapatkan perkiraan biaya "
"melalui konektor pengiriman. Kemudian, klik tombol :guilabel:`Tambahkan` "
"untuk menambahkan biaya pengiriman ke |SO| atau faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:262
msgid ":doc:`Charge customers for shipping after product delivery <invoicing>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kenakan biaya pengiriman kepada pelanggan setelah pengiriman produk "
"<invoicing>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:269
msgid ""
"For users making shipments without installing the *Sales* app, assign the "
"shipping carrier to the delivery order, by first going to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory` app. Then, from the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Overview` dashboard, select the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` operation type, "
"and choose the desired delivery order that is not already marked "
"as :guilabel:`Done` or :guilabel:`Cancelled`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk pengguna yang melakukan pengiriman tanpa menginstal aplikasi "
"*Penjualan*, tetapkan pengangkut pengiriman ke surat jalan, dengan terlebih "
"dahulu membuka aplikasi :menuselection:`Inventaris`. Kemudian, dari "
":guilabel:`Dashboard` Inventaris, pilih tipe operasi :guilabel:`Surat "
"Jalan`, dan pilih surat jalan yang diinginkan yang belum ditandai sebagai "
":guilabel:`Selesai` atau :guilabel:`Dibatalkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:275
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Additional info` tab, set the :guilabel:`Carrier` field to "
"the desired third-party shipping carrier. When the delivery method is set "
"to :ref:`production mode <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-"
"method>`, a :guilabel:`Tracking Reference` is provided."
msgstr ""
"Pada tab :guilabel:`Info tambahan`, atur kolom :guilabel:`Pengangkut` ke "
"pengangkut pengiriman pihak ketiga yang diinginkan. Ketika metode pengiriman "
"diatur ke :ref:`mode produksi <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"delivery-method>`, :guilabel:`Referensi Pelacakan` akan disediakan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:281
msgid ":doc:`Generate shipping labels <labels>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Buat label pengiriman <labels>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the delivery order's \"Additional info\" tab."
msgstr "Tampilkan tab \"Info tambahan\" pada surat jalan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:290
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Troubleshooting"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:292
msgid ""
"Since shipping connectors can sometimes be complex to set up, here are some "
"checks to try when things are not working as expected:"
msgstr ""
"Karena konektor pengiriman terkadang rumit untuk diatur, berikut adalah "
"beberapa pemeriksaan yang dapat dicoba ketika terjadi masalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:295
msgid ""
"Ensure the :ref:`warehouse information <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-source-address>` (e.g., address and phone number) in Odoo is "
"correct **and** matches the records saved in the shipping provider's website."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :ref:`informasi gudang <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"source-address>` (misalnya, alamat dan nomor telepon) di Odoo sudah benar "
"**dan** sesuai dengan catatan yang tersimpan di situs web penyedia "
"pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:298
msgid ""
"Verify that the :ref:`package type <inventory/warehouses_storage/package-"
"type>` and parameters are valid for the shipping carrier. To check, ensure "
"the shipment can be directly created on the shipping carrier's website."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :ref:`jenis paket <inventory/warehouses_storage/package-type>` dan "
"parameternya valid untuk pengiriman. Untuk memeriksanya, pastikan pengiriman "
"dapat langsung dibuat di website pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:301
msgid ""
"When encountering a price mismatch between Odoo's estimated cost and the "
"provider's charge, first ensure the delivery method is set "
"to :ref:`production environment <inventory/shipping_receiving/production-"
"env>`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika menghadapi ketidaksesuaian harga antara estimasi biaya Odoo dan biaya "
"penyedia layanan, pertama-tama pastikan metode pengiriman diatur ke "
":ref:`lingkungan produksi <inventory/shipping_receiving/production-env>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:305
msgid ""
"Then, create the shipment in both the carrier's website and Odoo, and verify "
"the prices are the same across Odoo, the shipping provider, and in the "
"*debug logs*."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, buat pengiriman di website pengiriman dan Odoo, lalu verifikasi "
"bahwa harganya sama di Odoo, penyedia layanan pengiriman, dan di *log debug*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:309
msgid ""
"When checking for a price mismatch in the debug logs, if the request says "
"the package weighs six kilograms, but the response from FedEx says the "
"package weights seven kilograms, it concludes that the issue is on FedEx's "
"side."
msgstr ""
"Ketika memeriksa ketidaksesuaian harga di log debug, jika permintaan "
"mengatakan paket memiliki berat enam kilogram, tetapi respons dari FedEx "
"mengatakan paket memiliki berat tujuh kilogram, dapat disimpulkan bahwa "
"masalahnya ada di pihak FedEx."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:314
msgid "Debug log"
msgstr "Log debug"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:316
msgid ""
"Track shipping data inconsistencies by activating debug logging. To do that, "
"go to the delivery method's configuration page (:menuselection:`Inventory "
"app --> Configuration --> Shipping Method`), and select the desired shipping "
"method. Click the :guilabel:`No Debugging` smart button to "
"activate :guilabel:`Debug Requests`."
msgstr ""
"Lacak ketidakkonsistenan data pengiriman dengan mengaktifkan pencatatan "
"debug. Untuk melakukannya, buka halaman konfigurasi metode pengiriman "
"(:menuselection:`aplikasi Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Metode Pengiriman`)"
", dan pilih metode pengiriman yang diinginkan. Klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`No Debugging` untuk mengaktifkan :guilabel:`Debug Requests`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"No Debug\" smart button."
msgstr "Tampilkan tombol pintar \"No Debug\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:325
msgid ""
"With :guilabel:`Debug Requests` activated, each time the shipping connector "
"is used to estimate the cost of shipping, records are saved in "
"the :guilabel:`Logging` report. To access the report, turn "
"on :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Database Structure section "
"--> Logging`."
msgstr ""
"Dengan :guilabel:`Debug Requests` diaktifkan, setiap kali konektor "
"pengiriman digunakan untuk memperkirakan biaya pengiriman, catatan akan "
"disimpan di laporan :guilabel:`Logging`. Untuk mengakses laporan tersebut, "
"aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>`, dan buka "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pengaturan --> Teknis --> bagian Struktur "
"Database --> Logging`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:331
msgid ""
"Logs are created for a shipping method each time the :ref:`Get Rate "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>` button is clicked "
"on :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` and invoices, **and** when a customer adds the "
"shipping carrier to their order through the *Website* app."
msgstr ""
"Log dibuat untuk metode pengiriman setiap kali tombol :ref:`Get Rate "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>` diklik pada :abbr:`SO "
"(Sales Orders)` dan faktur, **dan** ketika pelanggan menambahkan pengiriman "
"ke pesanan mereka melalui aplikasi *Website*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show how to find the \"Logging\" option from the \"Technical\" menu."
msgstr "Tampilkan cara menemukan opsi \"Logging\" dari menu \"Technical\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:340
msgid ""
"Click the *HTTP request* line item to open a detailed page, and verify the "
"correct information is sent from Odoo to the shipping carrier. In the *HTTP "
"response*, verify that the same information is received."
msgstr ""
"Klik item baris *HTTP request* untuk membuka halaman detail, dan verifikasi "
"bahwa informasi yang benar dikirim dari Odoo ke pengiriman. Di *HTTP "
"response*, verifikasi bahwa informasi yang sama diterima."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show debug request history in Settings > Technical > Logging."
msgstr "Tampilkan riwayat permintaan debug di Settings > Technical > Logging."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:3
msgid "UPS integration"
msgstr "Integrasi UPS"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:5
msgid ""
"UPS is a shipping carrier service that integrates with Odoo to coordinate "
"shipping to all regions. Once integrated, users can create shipping methods "
"that estimate shipping costs and :doc:`generate labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"UPS adalah layanan pengiriman yang terintegrasi dengan Odoo untuk "
"mengoordinasikan pengiriman ke semua wilayah. Setelah terintegrasi, pengguna "
"dapat membuat metode pengiriman yang memperkirakan biaya pengiriman dan "
":doc:`menghasilkan label <labels>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:12
msgid "To set up the UPS shipping connector in Odoo, complete these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur konektor pengiriman UPS di Odoo, selesaikan langkah-langkah "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:14
msgid ""
"Create a UPS account to get :ref:`account number <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-account-number>`"
msgstr ""
"Buat akun UPS untuk mendapatkan :ref:`nomor akun <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-account-number>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:16
msgid ""
"Create UPS developer account to get :ref:`client credentials <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-client-id>`"
msgstr ""
"Buat akun pengembang UPS untuk mendapatkan :ref:`kredensial klien <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-client-id>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:18
msgid "Set up shipping method in Odoo"
msgstr "Atur metode pengiriman di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:21
msgid ""
"When configuring a shipping method to use UPS, make sure "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` is set to :guilabel:`UPS`, **NOT** :guilabel:`UPS "
"Legacy`."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengonfigurasi metode pengiriman untuk menggunakan UPS, pastikan "
":guilabel:`Provider` diatur ke :guilabel:`UPS`, **BUKAN** :guilabel:`UPS "
"Legacy`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:24
msgid ""
"If shipping methods currently exist with the :guilabel:`Provider` set "
"to :guilabel:`UPS Legacy`, archive them, and create new shipping methods "
"using :guilabel:`UPS`, instead."
msgstr ""
"Jika metode pengiriman saat ini ada dengan :guilabel:`Provider` diatur ke "
":guilabel:`UPS Legacy`, arsipkan metode tersebut, dan buat metode pengiriman "
"baru menggunakan :guilabel:`UPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:28
msgid "UPS account setup"
msgstr "Pengaturan akun UPS"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:30
msgid ""
"To get started, go to the `UPS website <https://www.ups.com>`_ and click "
"the :guilabel:`Log In` button in the top-right corner to log in or create a "
"UPS account."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai, buka `situs web UPS <https://www.ups.com>`_ dan klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Log In` di sudut kanan atas untuk masuk atau membuat akun UPS."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:33
msgid ""
"After logging in, click the profile icon in the top-right corner, and "
"select :guilabel:`Accounts and Payment` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Setelah masuk, klik ikon profil di sudut kanan atas, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Accounts and Payment` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Show how to navigate to the \"Accounts and Payment\" page from the home "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan cara navigasi ke halaman \"Accounts and Payment\" dari layar "
"beranda."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:40
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Accounts and Payment Options` page, two accounts must be "
"configured: an Odoo shipment account and a payment card."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman :guilabel:`Accounts and Payment Options`, dua akun harus "
"dikonfigurasi: akun pengiriman Odoo dan kartu pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:44
msgid "Shipping account"
msgstr "Akun pengiriman"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:46
msgid ""
"To add an Odoo shipment account, select :guilabel:`Add New Account` from "
"the :guilabel:`Add a Payment Method` drop-down menu, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan akun pengiriman Odoo, pilih :guilabel:`Add New Account` "
"dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Add a Payment Method`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Add`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid "Display \"Add an account\" option from the drop-down menu."
msgstr "Tampilkan opsi \"Add an account\" dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:53
msgid ""
"On the next screen, labeled :guilabel:`Open a Shipping Account`, complete "
"the forms to configure the shipping account type (e.g. :guilabel:`Business`) "
"and if any regulated items will be shipped. Then finish the remaining three "
"steps in the wizard to :guilabel:`Add Addresses`, :guilabel:`Verify "
"Identity`, and :guilabel:`Explore Discounts`, with the last option being "
"optional."
msgstr ""
"Pada layar berikutnya, berlabel :guilabel:`Open a Shipping Account`, "
"lengkapi formulir untuk mengonfigurasi jenis akun pengiriman (mis. "
":guilabel:`Business`) dan apakah ada barang yang diatur akan dikirim. "
"Kemudian selesaikan tiga langkah yang tersisa dalam wizard untuk "
":guilabel:`Add Addresses`, :guilabel:`Verify Identity`, dan "
":guilabel:`Explore Discounts`, dengan opsi terakhir bersifat opsional."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:58
msgid ""
"When complete, submit the application on the last page of the wizard to "
"finish setting up the shipping account."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, kirim aplikasi di halaman terakhir wizard untuk "
"menyelesaikan pengaturan akun pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid "Display UPS form to fill out company shipping information."
msgstr "Tampilkan formulir UPS untuk mengisi informasi pengiriman perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:68
msgid "Get account number"
msgstr "Dapatkan nomor akun"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:70
msgid ""
"With the shipping account set up, the UPS :guilabel:`Account Number` becomes "
"available. To access it, navigate to :menuselection:`Profile --> Accounts "
"and Payment` and refer to the shipping account's :guilabel:`Number` field."
msgstr ""
"Dengan akun pengiriman yang sudah disiapkan, :guilabel:`Account Number` UPS "
"menjadi tersedia. Untuk mengaksesnya, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Profile --> Accounts and Payment` dan lihat field "
":guilabel:`Number` akun pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid "Show Account \"Number\" field for the shipping account."
msgstr "Tampilkan field \"Number\" Akun untuk akun pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:79
msgid "Payment card"
msgstr "Kartu pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:81
msgid ""
"Navigate back to the :guilabel:`Accounts and Payments` page and select "
"the :guilabel:`Add Payment Card` option from the :guilabel:`Add a Payment "
"Method` drop-down menu. Then, complete the form to add the credit card "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi kembali ke halaman :guilabel:`Accounts and Payments` dan pilih opsi "
":guilabel:`Add Payment Card` dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Add a Payment "
"Method`. Kemudian, lengkapi formulir untuk menambahkan informasi kartu "
"kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid "Show \"Add Payment Card\" option from the drop-down."
msgstr "Tampilkan opsi \"Add Payment Card\" dari drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:90
msgid "UPS developer account setup"
msgstr "Pengaturan akun developer UPS"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:92
msgid ""
"Next, log into the `UPS developer account <http://developer.ups.com/>`_ to "
"generate the developer key. To begin, click the profile icon in the top-"
"right corner, and choose the :guilabel:`Apps` option from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, masuk ke `akun developer UPS <http://developer.ups.com/>`_ "
"untuk menghasilkan kunci developer. Untuk memulai, klik ikon profil di sudut "
"kanan atas, dan pilih opsi :guilabel:`Apps` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Display the \"Apps\" drop-down option after clicking the profile picture "
"icon."
msgstr "Tampilkan opsi drop-down \"Apps\" setelah mengklik ikon gambar profil."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:101
msgid "Add app"
msgstr "Tambah aplikasi"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:103
