#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:305
msgid "Vendor lead time"
msgstr "Waktu tunggu vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:307
msgid ""
"To set a vendor lead time for orders arriving in the warehouse from a vendor "
"location, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products --> "
"Products`. Select the desired product, and switch to "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab. In the editable vendor :guilabel:`Purchase` "
"tab to add a pricelist. Click the :guilabel:`Add a line` button to add "
"vendor details, such as the :guilabel:`Vendor` name, :guilabel:`Unit Price` "
"offered for the product, and lastly, the :guilabel:`Lead Time`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur waktu tunggu vendor untuk pesanan yang tiba di gudang dari "
"lokasi vendor, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pembelian --> "
"Produk --> Produk`. Pilih produk yang diinginkan, dan beralih ke tab "
":guilabel:`Pembelian`. Di tab vendor :guilabel:`Pembelian` yang dapat diedit "
"untuk menambahkan daftar harga. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Tambah baris` untuk "
"menambahkan detail vendor, seperti nama :guilabel:`Vendor`, :guilabel:`Harga "
"Satuan` yang ditawarkan untuk produk, dan terakhir, :guilabel:`Waktu Tunggu`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:314
msgid ""
"Multiple vendors and lead times can be added to the vendor pricelist. The "
"default vendor and lead time selected is the entry at the top of the list."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa vendor dan waktu tunggu dapat ditambahkan ke daftar harga vendor. "
"Vendor dan waktu tunggu default yang dipilih adalah entri di bagian atas "
"daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:318
msgid ""
"On the vendor pricelist of the product form, the :guilabel:`Lead Time` for "
"the selected vendor is set to `10 days.`"
msgstr ""
"Pada daftar harga vendor dari formulir produk, :guilabel:`Waktu Tunggu` "
"untuk vendor yang dipilih diatur menjadi `10 hari.`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid "Add lead times in the Purchase tab of a product form."
msgstr "Tambahkan waktu tunggu di tab Pembelian dari formulir produk."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:327
msgid "Days to purchase"
msgstr "Hari untuk membeli"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:329
msgid ""
"*Days to purchase* affects **only** replenishment methods that "
"use :doc:`pull rules <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes>`—"
"for example :doc:`reordering rules <reordering_rules>` or :doc:`make to "
"order (MTO) <mto>`. It does not change the interval between *Order Deadline* "
"and *Expected Arrival*."
msgstr ""
"*Hari untuk membeli* memengaruhi **hanya** metode pengisian ulang yang "
"menggunakan :doc:`aturan tarik <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"use_routes>`—misalnya :doc:`aturan pemesanan ulang <reordering_rules>` atau "
":doc:`buat berdasarkan pesanan (MTO) <mto>`. Ini tidak mengubah interval "
"antara *Batas Waktu Pesanan* dan *Perkiraan Kedatangan*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:334
msgid ""
"To set it up, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Advanced Scheduling` section, in "
"the :guilabel:`Days to Purchase` field, specify the number of days required "
"for the vendor to confirm a |RFQ| after receiving it from the company."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaturnya, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Inventaris --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Penjadwalan "
"Lanjutan`, di bidang :guilabel:`Hari untuk Pembelian`, tentukan jumlah hari "
"yang diperlukan vendor untuk mengonfirmasi |RFQ| setelah menerimanya dari "
"perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:341
msgid "Global example"
msgstr "Contoh global"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:343
msgid ""
"See the following example to understand how all the lead times work together "
"to ensure timely order fulfillment:"
msgstr ""
"Lihat contoh berikut untuk memahami bagaimana semua waktu tunggu bekerja "
"sama untuk memastikan pemenuhan pesanan tepat waktu:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:346
msgid "**Sales security lead time**: 1 day"
msgstr "**Waktu tunggu keamanan penjualan**: 1 hari"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:347
msgid "**Manufacturing lead time**: 3 days"
msgstr "**Waktu tunggu manufaktur**: 3 hari"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:348
msgid "**Vendor lead time**: 4 days"
msgstr "**Waktu tunggu vendor**: 4 hari"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:349
msgid "**Days to purchase**: 1 day"
msgstr "**Hari untuk membeli**: 1 hari"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:351
msgid ""
"The customer places an order for a manufactured product on August 1, and the "
"scheduled delivery date from the warehouse is on August 11. Odoo uses lead "
"times and automated reordering rules to schedule the necessary operations, "
"based on the outgoing shipment delivery date of August 11:"
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan melakukan pesanan untuk produk yang diproduksi pada 1 Agustus, dan "
"tanggal pengiriman terjadwal dari gudang adalah pada 11 Agustus. Odoo "
"menggunakan waktu tunggu dan aturan pemesanan ulang otomatis untuk "
"menjadwalkan operasi yang diperlukan, berdasarkan tanggal pengiriman keluar "
"pada 11 Agustus:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid ""
"Show timeline of how lead times work together to schedule warehouse "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan timeline bagaimana waktu tunggu bekerja sama untuk menjadwalkan "
"operasi gudang."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:358
msgid "**August 1**: Sales order created, confirmed by salesperson."
msgstr "**1 Agustus**: Sales Order dibuat, dikonfirmasi oleh tenaga penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:360
msgid ""
"**August 2**: Deadline to order components to ensure they arrive in time "
"when manufacturing begins (4-day supplier lead time)."
msgstr ""
"**2 Agustus**: Batas waktu untuk memesan komponen untuk memastikan komponen "
"tiba tepat waktu saat manufaktur dimulai (waktu tunggu pemasok 4 hari)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:363
msgid "**August 7**: Scheduled date of receipt for components."
msgstr "**7 Agustus**: Tanggal penerimaan terjadwal untuk komponen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:365
msgid ""
"**August 7**: Deadline to begin manufacturing. Calculated by subtracting the "
"manufacturing lead time of 3 days from the expected delivery date of August "
"10."
msgstr ""
"**7 Agustus**: Batas waktu untuk memulai manufaktur. Dihitung dengan "
"mengurangi waktu tunggu manufaktur 3 hari dari tanggal pengiriman yang "
"diharapkan pada 10 Agustus."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:368
msgid ""
"**August 10**: :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` on the delivery order form "
"indicates the updated expected delivery date. Originally set as August 11, "
"but the sales security lead time pushes the date forward by a day."
msgstr ""
"**10 Agustus**: :guilabel:`Tanggal Terjadwal` pada formulir surat jalan "
"menunjukkan tanggal pengiriman yang diharapkan yang telah diperbarui. "
"Awalnya ditetapkan sebagai 11 Agustus, tetapi waktu tunggu keamanan "
"penjualan memajukan tanggal satu hari."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:372
msgid ""
"Odoo's replenishment planning maps a business' order fulfillment process, "
"setting pre-determined deadlines and raw material order dates, including "
"buffer days for potential delays. This ensures products are delivered on "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Perencanaan pengisian ulang Odoo memetakan proses pemenuhan pesanan bisnis, "
"menetapkan tenggat waktu yang telah ditentukan dan tanggal pesanan bahan "
"baku, termasuk hari penyangga untuk potensi keterlambatan. Ini memastikan "
"produk dikirim tepat waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:3
msgid "Replenish on order (MTO)"
msgstr "Isi ulang berdasarkan pesanan (MTO)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:13
msgid ""
"*Replenish on order*, also known as *MTO* (make to order), is a "
"replenishment strategy that creates a draft order every time a product is "
"needed to fulfill a sales order (SO) or as a component in a manufacturing "
"order (MO)."
msgstr ""
"*Isi ulang berdasarkan pesanan*, juga dikenal sebagai *MTO* (make to order), "
"adalah strategi pengisian ulang yang membuat draft pesanan setiap kali "
"produk diperlukan untuk memenuhi sales order (SO) atau sebagai komponen "
"dalam manufacturing order (MO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:17
msgid ""
"For :doc:`purchased products <../../../purchase/manage_deals/rfq>`, Odoo "
"creates an |RFQ|."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :doc:`produk yang dibeli <../../../purchase/manage_deals/rfq>`, Odoo "
"membuat |RFQ|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:18
msgid ""
"For :doc:`manufactured products <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/"
"configure_manufacturing_product>`, it creates an |MO|."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :doc:`produk yang diproduksi <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/"
"configure_manufacturing_product>`, Odoo membuat |MO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:21
msgid ""
"If stock is available, no |RFQ| or |MO| is generated and the sale proceeds "
"normally. Otherwise, the |RFQ| or |MO| is generated and directly linked to "
"the originating |SO| through a smart button."
msgstr ""
"Jika stok tersedia, tidak ada |RFQ| atau |MO| yang dihasilkan dan penjualan "
"berlanjut secara normal. Jika tidak, |RFQ| atau |MO| dihasilkan dan langsung "
"ditautkan ke |SO| asal melalui tombol pintar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:24
msgid ""
"This approach offers clear traceability, since each |RFQ| or |MO| is tied "
"back to its demand."
msgstr ""
"Pendekatan ini menawarkan keterlacakan yang jelas, karena setiap |RFQ| atau "
"|MO| terkait kembali ke permintaannya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:27
msgid ""
"The |RFQ| or |MO| generated by |MTO| is designed to fulfill the originating |"
"SO|. These documents should normally be confirmed or adjusted rather than "
"canceled. If the demand changes, update the document instead of canceling it."
msgstr ""
"|RFQ| atau |MO| yang dihasilkan oleh |MTO| dirancang untuk memenuhi |SO| "
"asal. Dokumen ini biasanya harus dikonfirmasi atau disesuaikan, bukan "
"dibatalkan. Jika permintaan berubah, perbarui dokumen alih-alih "
"membatalkannya."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:32
msgid ""
"If an |RFQ| or |MO| is canceled, Odoo does not automatically generate a "
"replacement. A new replenishment document must be created manually, but it "
"**cannot** be linked back to the original |SO| through the smart button."
msgstr ""
"Jika |RFQ| atau |MO| dibatalkan, Odoo tidak secara otomatis membuat "
"penggantinya. Dokumen pengisian ulang baru harus dibuat secara manual, "
"tetapi **tidak dapat** dihubungkan kembali ke |SO| asli melalui tombol "
"pintar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:36
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Save` to save the change."
msgstr "Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Simpan` untuk menyimpan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:46
msgid "Enable the MTO route"
msgstr "Aktifkan rute MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:48
msgid ""
"In order to use the |MTO| route, the :guilabel:`Replenish on order (MTO)` "
"setting must be enabled. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app "
"--> Configuration --> Settings`. Go to the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section at "
"the end of the page, and select the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Replenish on "
"order (MTO)`. Click :guilabel:`Save` to confirm the setting."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan rute |MTO|, pengaturan :guilabel:`Isi ulang saat order "
"(MTO)` harus diaktifkan. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Buka bagian :guilabel:`Gudang` "
"di akhir halaman, dan pilih kotak centang di samping :guilabel:`Isi ulang "
"saat order (MTO)`. Klik :guilabel:`Simpan` untuk mengonfirmasi pengaturan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:None
msgid "Select the Replenish on order (MTO) checkbox."
msgstr "Pilih kotak centang Isi ulang saat order (MTO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:59
msgid "Configure a product for MTO"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan produk untuk MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:61
msgid ""
"With the |MTO| route enabled, products can now be configured to use "
"replenish on order. To do so, begin by going to :menuselection:`Inventory "
"app --> Products --> Products`, then select an existing product, or "
"click :guilabel:`New` to configure a new product."
msgstr ""
"Dengan rute |MTO| diaktifkan, produk sekarang dapat dikonfigurasikan untuk "
"menggunakan isi ulang saat order. Untuk melakukannya, mulailah dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Inventaris --> Produk --> Produk`, lalu "
"pilih produk yang ada, atau klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk mengonfigurasikan "
"produk baru."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:65
msgid ""
"In the product form, go to the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab. Under the "
"*Operations* section, select the checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Replenish "
"on Order (MTO)` option in the :guilabel:`Routes` field."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir produk, buka tab :guilabel:`Inventaris`. Di bawah bagian "
"*Operations*, pilih kotak centang di samping opsi :guilabel:`Replenish on "
"Order (MTO)` di kolom :guilabel:`Routes`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:69
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Replenish on Order (MTO)` route does not work if "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` route is enabled. To ensure the product is "
"configured for manufacturing, make sure the checkbox next to "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` route is not selected."
msgstr ""
"Rute :guilabel:`Replenish on Order (MTO)` tidak berfungsi jika rute "
":guilabel:`Pembelian` diaktifkan. Untuk memastikan produk dikonfigurasi "
"untuk manufaktur, pastikan kotak centang di samping rute "
":guilabel:`Pembelian` tidak dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:None
msgid "Select the MTO route and a second route on the Inventory tab."
msgstr "Pilih rute MTO dan rute kedua pada tab Inventaris."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:77
msgid ""
"If the product is purchased from a vendor to fulfill |SOs|, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Can be Purchased` checkbox under the product name. Doing so "
"makes the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab appear alongside the other tabs below."
msgstr ""
"Jika produk dibeli dari vendor untuk memenuhi |SOs|, aktifkan kotak centang "
":guilabel:`Can be Purchased` di bawah nama produk. Dengan melakukan ini, tab "
":guilabel:`Pembelian` akan muncul di samping tab lainnya di bawah."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab and specify a :guilabel:`Vendor` and "
"the :guilabel:`Price` they sell the product for."
msgstr ""
"Klik tab :guilabel:`Pembelian` dan tentukan :guilabel:`Vendor` serta "
":guilabel:`Harga` yang mereka jual untuk produk tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:85
msgid ""
"Specifying a vendor is essential for this workflow, because Odoo cannot "
"generate an |RFQ| without knowing who the product is purchased from."
msgstr ""
"Menentukan vendor sangat penting untuk alur kerja ini, karena Odoo tidak "
"dapat menghasilkan |RFQ| tanpa mengetahui dari siapa produk dibeli."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:88
msgid ""
"If the product is manufactured, make sure it has a bill of materials (BOM) "
"configured for it. To do so, click the :guilabel:`Bill of Materials` smart "
"button at the top of the screen, then click :guilabel:`New` on "
"the :guilabel:`Bill of Materials` page to configure a new |BOM| for the "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Jika produk diproduksi, pastikan produk tersebut memiliki bill of materials "
"(BOM) yang dikonfigurasi. Untuk melakukannya, klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Bill of Materials` di bagian atas layar, kemudian klik "
":guilabel:`New` pada halaman :guilabel:`Bill of Materials` untuk "
"mengonfigurasi |BOM| baru untuk produk tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:93
msgid ""
"For a full overview of |BOM| creation, see the documentation on :doc:`bills "
"of materials <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/bill_configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk gambaran lengkap tentang pembuatan |BOM|, lihat dokumentasi tentang "
":doc:`bills of materials <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/"
"bill_configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:99
msgid "Replenish using MTO"
msgstr "Isi ulang menggunakan MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:101
msgid ""
"After configuring a product to use the |MTO| route, a replenishment order is "
"created for it every time an |SO| or |MO| including the product is "
"confirmed. The type of order created depends on the second route selected in "
"addition to |MTO|."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengonfigurasi produk untuk menggunakan rute |MTO|, pesanan "
"pengisian ulang dibuat setiap kali |SO| atau |MO| yang menyertakan produk "
"tersebut dikonfirmasi. Jenis pesanan yang dibuat tergantung pada rute kedua "
"yang dipilih selain |MTO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:105
msgid ""
"For example, if *Buy* was the second route selected, then a |PO| is created "
"upon confirmation of an |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, jika *Buy* adalah rute kedua yang dipilih, maka |PO| dibuat "
"setelah konfirmasi |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:109
msgid ""
"When the |MTO| route is enabled for a product, a replenishment order is "
"always created upon confirmation of an |SO| or |MO|. This is the case, even "
"if there is enough stock of the product on-hand to fulfill the |SO|, without "
"buying or manufacturing additional units of it."
msgstr ""
"Ketika rute |MTO| diaktifkan untuk produk, pesanan pengisian ulang selalu "
"dibuat setelah konfirmasi |SO| atau |MO|. Hal ini terjadi, bahkan jika ada "
"stok produk yang cukup untuk memenuhi |SO|, tanpa membeli atau memproduksi "
"unit tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:113
msgid ""
"While the |MTO| route can be used in unison with the *Buy* or *Manufacture* "
"routes, the *Buy* route is used as the example for this workflow. Begin by "
"navigating to the :menuselection:`Sales` app, then click :guilabel:`New`, "
"which opens a blank quotation form."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun rute |MTO| dapat digunakan bersama dengan rute *Buy* atau "
"*Manufacture*, rute *Buy* digunakan sebagai contoh untuk alur kerja ini. "
"Mulailah dengan membuka aplikasi :menuselection:`Penjualan`, kemudian klik "
":guilabel:`New`, yang akan membuka formulir penawaran kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:117
msgid ""
"On the blank quotation form, add a :guilabel:`Customer`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a product` under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and "
"enter a product configured to use the *MTO* and *Buy* routes. "
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm`, and the quotation is turned into an |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir penawaran kosong, tambahkan :guilabel:`Customer`. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Add a product` di bawah tab :guilabel:`Order Lines`, dan "
"masukkan produk yang dikonfigurasi untuk menggunakan rute *MTO* dan *Buy*. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Confirm`, dan penawaran akan berubah menjadi |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:121
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Purchase` smart button now appears at the top of the page. "
"Clicking it opens the |RFQ| associated with the |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Tombol pintar :guilabel:`Pembelian` sekarang muncul di bagian atas halaman. "
"Mengkliknya akan membuka |RFQ| yang terkait dengan |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:124
msgid ""
"After receiving approval from the vendor that they can meet the demand by "
"the :guilabel:`Expected Arrival` date, click :guilabel:`Confirm Order` to "
"turn it into a |PO|. A purple :guilabel:`Receive Products` button now "
"appears above the |PO|. Once the products are received, "
"click :guilabel:`Receive Products` to open the receipt order, and "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to enter the products into inventory."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menerima persetujuan dari vendor bahwa mereka dapat memenuhi "
"permintaan pada tanggal :guilabel:`Expected Arrival`, klik "
":guilabel:`Confirm Order` untuk mengubahnya menjadi |PO|. Tombol ungu "
":guilabel:`Receive Products` sekarang muncul di atas |PO|. Setelah produk "
"diterima, klik :guilabel:`Receive Products` untuk membuka pesanan "
"penerimaan, dan klik :guilabel:`Validate` untuk memasukkan produk ke dalam "
"inventaris."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:130
msgid ""
"Return to the |SO| by clicking the :guilabel:`SO` breadcrumb, or by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Orders`, and "
"selecting the |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Kembali ke |SO| dengan mengklik breadcrumb :guilabel:`SO`, atau dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Penjualan --> Pesanan --> Pesanan`, dan "
"memilih |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:133
msgid ""
"Finally, click the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button at the top of the order "
"to open the delivery order. Once the products have been shipped to the "
"customer, click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Delivery` di bagian atas pesanan "
"untuk membuka surat jalan. Setelah produk dikirim ke pelanggan, klik "
":guilabel:`Validate` untuk mengonfirmasi pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:140
msgid "Cancel an MTO sales order"
msgstr "Batalkan sales order MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:142
msgid ""
"When a |SO| that had created an |RFQ| or |MO| is canceled, the related "
"delivery order is canceled automatically. However, the |RFQ| or |MO| "
"themselves are **not** canceled. Instead, a warning appears in their chatter "
"noting the |SO| cancellation. These documents remain active, so the user can "
"either cancel them manually or repurpose the replenishment for another order."
msgstr ""
"Ketika |SO| yang telah membuat |RFQ| atau |MO| dibatalkan, surat jalan "
"terkait akan dibatalkan secara otomatis. Namun, |RFQ| atau |MO| itu sendiri "
"**tidak** dibatalkan. Sebaliknya, peringatan muncul di chatter mereka yang "
"mencatat pembatalan |SO|. Dokumen-dokumen ini tetap aktif, sehingga pengguna "
"dapat membatalkannya secara manual atau menggunakan kembali pengisian ulang "
"untuk pesanan lain."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:148
msgid ""
"For information on workflows that include the |MTO| route, see the following "
"documentation:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi tentang alur kerja yang menyertakan rute |MTO|, lihat "
"dokumentasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:150
msgid ":doc:`resupply_warehouses`"
msgstr ":doc:`resupply_warehouses`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`../../../manufacturing/subcontracting/subcontracting_basic`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../manufacturing/subcontracting/subcontracting_basic`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:152
msgid ":doc:`../../../manufacturing/advanced_configuration/sub_assemblies`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../manufacturing/advanced_configuration/sub_assemblies`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:17
msgid ""
"*Reordering rules* are used to keep forecasted stock levels above a certain "
"threshold without exceeding a specified upper limit. This is accomplished by "
"specifying a minimum quantity that stock should not fall below and a maximum "
"quantity that stock should not exceed."
msgstr ""
"*Aturan pemesanan ulang* digunakan untuk menjaga tingkat stok yang "
"diperkirakan di atas ambang batas tertentu tanpa melebihi batas atas yang "
"ditentukan. Hal ini dicapai dengan menentukan kuantitas minimum yang tidak "
"boleh turun di bawahnya dan kuantitas maksimum yang tidak boleh dilampaui "
"oleh stok."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:21
msgid ""
"Reordering rules can be configured for each product based on the route used "
"to replenish it. If a product uses the *Buy* route, then a *request for "
"quotation* (RFQ) is created when the reordering rule is triggered. If a "
"product uses the *Manufacture* route, then a *manufacturing order* (MO) is "
"created instead. This is the case regardless of the selected replenishment "
"route."
msgstr ""
"Aturan pemesanan ulang dapat dikonfigurasi untuk setiap produk berdasarkan "
"rute yang digunakan untuk mengisi ulangnya. Jika produk menggunakan rute "
"*Buy*, maka *request for quotation* (RFQ) dibuat ketika aturan pemesanan "
"ulang dipicu. Jika produk menggunakan rute *Manufacture*, maka "
"*manufacturing order* (MO) dibuat sebagai gantinya. Hal ini terjadi terlepas "
"dari rute pengisian ulang yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:27
