#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:3
msgid "Pass - Fail quality check"
msgstr "Pemeriksaan kualitas Pass - Fail"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:9
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Quality*, a *Pass - Fail* check is one of the quality check types "
"that can be selected when creating a new quality check or quality control "
"point (QCP). *Pass - Fail* checks consist of a text field that allows the "
"creator to specify a certain criteria that a product must meet to pass the "
"check."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo *Quality*, pemeriksaan *Pass - Fail* adalah salah satu jenis "
"pemeriksaan kualitas yang dapat dipilih saat membuat pemeriksaan kualitas "
"atau quality control point (QCP) baru. Pemeriksaan *Pass - Fail* terdiri "
"dari kolom teks yang memungkinkan pembuat menentukan kriteria tertentu yang "
"harus dipenuhi produk agar lulus pemeriksaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:15
msgid "Create a Pass - Fail quality check"
msgstr "Membuat pemeriksaan kualitas Pass - Fail"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:17
msgid ""
"There are two distinct ways that *Pass - Fail* quality checks can be "
"created. A single check can be manually created. Alternatively, a |QCP| can "
"be configured that automatically creates checks at a predetermined interval."
msgstr ""
"Ada dua cara berbeda untuk membuat pemeriksaan kualitas *Pass - Fail*. Satu "
"pemeriksaan dapat dibuat secara manual. Atau, |QCP| dapat dikonfigurasi "
"untuk membuat pemeriksaan secara otomatis pada interval yang telah "
"ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:21
msgid ""
"This documentation only details the configuration options that are unique to "
"*Pass - Fail* quality checks and |QCPs|. For a full overview of all the "
"configuration options available when creating a single check or a |QCP|, see "
"the documentation on :ref:`quality checks <quality/quality_management/"
"quality-checks>` and :ref:`quality control points <quality/"
"quality_management/quality-control-points>`."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentasi ini hanya merinci opsi konfigurasi yang unik untuk pemeriksaan "
"kualitas *Pass - Fail* dan |QCPs|. Untuk gambaran lengkap tentang semua opsi "
"konfigurasi yang tersedia saat membuat satu pemeriksaan atau |QCP|, lihat "
"dokumentasi tentang :ref:`quality checks <quality/quality_management/quality-"
"checks>` dan :ref:`quality control points <quality/quality_management/"
"quality-control-points>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:30
msgid ""
"To create a single *Pass - Fail* quality check, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality Checks`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Fill out the new quality check form as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat satu pemeriksaan kualitas *Pass - Fail*, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality Checks`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`New`. Isi formulir pemeriksaan kualitas baru sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:51
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Type` drop-down field, select the :guilabel:`Pass - Fail` "
"quality check type."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom drop-down :guilabel:`Type`, pilih jenis pemeriksaan kualitas "
":guilabel:`Pass - Fail`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:37
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Instructions` text field of the :guilabel:`Notes` tab, "
"enter instructions for how to complete the quality check and the criteria "
"that must be met for the check to pass."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom teks :guilabel:`Instructions` pada tab :guilabel:`Notes`, masukkan "
"instruksi tentang cara menyelesaikan pemeriksaan kualitas dan kriteria yang "
"harus dipenuhi agar pemeriksaan lulus."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:None
msgid "A quality check form configured for a Pass - Fail quality check."
msgstr ""
"Formulir pemeriksaan kualitas yang dikonfigurasi untuk pemeriksaan kualitas "
"Pass - Fail."

